snippet.title: How to go from Military to iOS Developer in San Francisco with Sean Allen
snippet.description:
Today we have a special guest with us, Sean Allen, who is also a fellow YouTuber and iOS Developer.  In this video, I interview Sean about his experience as a busy contractor in the San Francisco area.  He'll also be sharing his unique experience of how he started in the military years ago and made his way into iOS development today.  Finally, Sean gives us his advice on getting into programming as a beginner and all the things to watch out for.

You can find Sean below:
https://youtube.com/seanallen
https://twitter.com/SeanA0400
